;; Zone file: littlelightsstudio.at
;; Generated:  2026-04-27 — easyname-Migration mit Cleanup
;; Target:     Hetzner Cloud Console → DNS → Add DNS zone → Import zone file
;;
;; Google Workspace Domain. easyname-Webspace-Anteil entfernt (Wildcard raus),
;; Mail-Stack (Google) ergänzt um DKIM + DMARC.
;;
;; Cleanup (siehe docs/dns-zones/README.md):
;;   ENTFERNT: *
;;   BEHALTEN: A root + www (verweist auf easyname-Webspace, Subdomain-Tab leer)
;;   ERGÄNZT:  Google DKIM (google._domainkey), DMARC (_dmarc)

$ORIGIN littlelightsstudio.at.
$TTL 3600

; ── Web (easyname Webspace, kein Subdomain-Tab) ───────────────
@                    IN  A      77.244.243.53
www                  IN  A      77.244.243.53

; ── Mail Records (Google Workspace) ───────────────────────────
@                    IN  MX     1 smtp.google.com.
@                    IN  TXT    "google-site-verification=WLLcabbxKJTk_YcqL2KC00AFDxi8KOWpJWAjyn503OM"
@                    IN  TXT    "v=spf1 include:_spf.google.com ~all"

; Google DKIM (User-geliefert aus Admin Console)
google._domainkey    IN  TXT    "v=DKIM1; k=rsa; "

; DMARC — Monitoring-Modus, Reports an admin@littlelights.studio
_dmarc               IN  TXT    "v=DMARC1; p=none; rua=mailto:admin@littlelights.studio"
